dcterms:description: The YCB video dataset is used for training and testing with the original train/test split. It contains 133,827 frames of 21 objects selected from the YCB object set with 6D pose annotation, along with 80,000 frames of synthetic data as an extension to the training set.
dcterms:title: YCB video dataset

dcterms:description: The YCB object set is used for benchmarking in manipulation research, providing a collection of objects and models for various robotic tasks.
